  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Galactic Seals Survivors is a survival game with minimalistic gameplay and roguelike elements. You are a galactic seal, and seals face many dangerous obstacles in life. You are fighting the galactic orcas; these brutal and intelligent beings only see seals as a source of nourishment. Fight your way through 10 levels and obtain credits to spend on upgrades in order to reach and defeat the final boss in the Cyber City.</p>",
